{"tid":406703,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"(野人生活）幾年後想試吓體驗野人生活，求連登仔意見","createTime":"2017-09-20T00:59:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-20T02:33:18.000Z","uid":143652,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"845704c9f3155c528eb9f4dfaa163ce5762685f2","tid":406703,"uid":143652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T00:59:22.000Z","msg":"話說小弟想自己一個人想獨立生活，但你知香港租金已經去到天文數字，一個月已經俾租金食咗一大半。時下年青人都係想有安樂窩都難。但我問自己為何唔想吓露宿？<br />\n<br />\n小弟想搵個山頭露營生活，即係自己搭個營，水同電都缺少嘅情況吓生活。然而要好似正常人咁返工，放工之後要係太陽落山前上山搭營<br />\n<br />\n各位連登仔認為有無得諗，俾吓意見當支持小弟"},{"pid":"4ecd078347dd011f54cd0750a2f956e976d4b108","tid":406703,"uid":51978,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T01:02:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"edc02d1c6d2dd6ce08b09af590556f69866a6d5e","tid":406703,"uid":143652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T01:05:59.000Z","msg":"以下想請教嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位巴打覺得邊個山頭適合來往市區？<br />\n<br />\n長期住係山頭有沒有犯法<br />\n<br />\n遇到山賊同鬼有咩辦法解決<br />\n<br />\n有咩野外求生技能係要識"},{"pid":"01c366359520ca2a9570ba7b295c026b7abc1722","tid":406703,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T01:07:10.000Z","msg":"包你三日內放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19ae797132ae7ce749e71dd9145bd89532bef1ee","tid":406703,"uid":143652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T01:09:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>包你三日內放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c714c8b05bc145cdc61e044be3cdc64ae8082b9","tid":406703,"uid":5945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T02:12:51.000Z","msg":"大帽山扶輪公園營地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a37c5286e33d5597919572e99440e11b845bec","tid":406703,"uid":132524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T02:29:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話說小弟想自己一個人想獨立生活，但你知香港租金已經去到天文數字，一個月已經俾租金食咗一大半。時下年青人都係想有安樂窩都難。但我問自己為何唔想吓露宿？<br />\n<br />\n小弟想搵個山頭露營生活，即係自己搭個營，水同電都缺少嘅情況吓生活。然而要好似正常人咁返工，放工之後要係太陽落山前上山搭營<br />\n<br />\n各位連登仔認為有無得諗，俾吓意見當支持小弟</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n留明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beff4bfb55c30bb68b036cf0a0244a7b00dae30e","tid":406703,"uid":69419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T02:33:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCAL3JXZSzSm8AlZyD3nQdBA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCAL3JXZSzSm8AlZyD3nQdBA&d=JFlsvJM%2Ft%2FzLb4bQ1ssAGjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=36d69f4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCAL3JXZSzSm8AlZyD3nQdBA</a><br />\n<br />\n你可以跟佢玩下"}]}